=\"2832px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hxdyl</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Given all the rhetoric about AI-based power demand, and the fact that The Utilities Select Sector SPDR Fund ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLU\" title=\"The Utilities Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF\">XLU</a></span>) is +33% over the past year, many investors may be under the impression that utility stocks are significantly over-valued. That is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741649-xlu-utility-stocks-have-just-begun-their-ai-driven-assent", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 10:59:23"}, {"id": "4741648", "title": "Great Lakes Dredge & Dock Is A Steal With Crystal Clear Visibility And Massive Growth Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"trailing suction hopper dredger creating land\" data-id=\"1750092977\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bjoern Wylezich/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Great Lakes Dredge &amp; Dock Corp. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLDD\" title=\"Great Lakes Dredge &amp; Dock Corporation\">GLDD</a></span>) is an $850 million dredging services provider with a legacy tracing back to the 1890s. For those who are unaware, dredging refers to the process of excavating sediment or</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750092977/image_1750092977.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741648-great-lakes-dredge-and-dock-is-a-steal-with-crystal-clear-visibility-and-massive-growth-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 10:54:51"}, {"id": "4741646", "title": "Hertz Global Holdings: Weak Financially And Lags Industry Trends", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"sign with arrow point to rent a car service at the airport for passenger who want to hide a car for travel around city. freedom transportation for convenient travel\" data-id=\"926104828\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-capti